<article class="post--single post-1846 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-cakes category-desserts category-perennial-favorite category-snacks category-vegetarian tag-france tag-french tag-yogurt-cake ingredients-eggs ingredients-lemon ingredients-yogurt" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/BlogPosting">
