    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Janet, that&#39;s a good question.  The cake will not hold all of the syrup without dripping, no.  I still go ahead and pour it all, because I like the tartness and moisture it gives, but there&#39;s usually some syrup that flows over the edge of the cake and isn&#39;t absorbed.</p>
