    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Hi Molly! I love all your recipes. I tried making this cake a few days back. It came out great &#8211; moist and golden. However, the glaze made it very sour! Almost inedible, in fact. Could my lemons be the culprit? I used the juice of two lemons and 1/4 cup of icing sugar, like you had mentioned in the recipe.</p>
